This project implements an **end-to-end Automatic License Plate Recognition (ALPR) system** capable of detecting vehicles and recognizing license plates from **real-time camera feeds** as well as **uploaded images/videos**.

The system integrates **deep learningâ€“based object detection**, **OCR**, and a **web-based interface** to deliver a practical, scalable, and production-oriented ALPR solution.

