---

## ğŸ§ª Model Details

### Vehicle Detection

* **Model:** YOLOv8 (COCO pretrained)
* **Classes:** Car, Bus, Truck, Motorcycle

### License Plate Detection

* **Model:** YOLOv8 (Custom-trained)
* **Dataset:** UFPR-ALPR / OpenALPR (YOLO format)
* **Training:** Transfer learning from YOLOv8n

### OCR

* **Engine:** EasyOCR
* **Filtering:** Confidence thresholding (> 0.6)

